Details: The AICTE Pragati Scholarship Scheme is a financial assistance program for girl students in technical courses at AICTE-approved institutions. The scholarship is awarded to meritorious students from families with an annual income of less than ₹8,00,000. Selected students receive ₹50,000 per year for up to three years.
Eligibility: Female student; Admitted to first-year diploma/degree or second-year through lateral entry; Family income less than ₹8,00,000; Max two girls per family.
